title: About Eva
text:
🎓 What I Do
I’m the PR Manager for the Investment Club, a Money Mentor, and a proud SGA Senator. I love creating visuals that communicate data beautifully, and I work hard to back every design with sharp, analytical thinking.

title: About Eva
text:
🌸 Who I Am
Every day starts with a cup of matcha 🍵 and the latest issue of VOGUE — because style matters, even in stats!
If i’m not in class, work or at a meeting, you can find me at home in the gym, or studying in the library. Whether I’m curating Pinterest boards or debugging R/ JAVA code, I am always hard at work.
